Subject: Fedora Roadmap
Description: Take a look at one of the premiere Linux distributions which serves as the testing ground for Red Hat Linux.  Speakers include:Tom Callaway - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: Raspberry Pi Hacks
Description: Ruth Suehle and Tom Callaway will talk about the $35 mini-computer, how it works, and give lots of ideas and inspirations on what you can do with it. They are the co-authors of the O'Reilly book 'Raspberry Pi Hacks', and generally do all sorts of things with the credit-card sized computer that are fun and warranty voiding.  Speakers include:Tom Callaway, Ruth Suehle - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes
